original_title: US-backed Gaza Humanitarian Foundation launches aid reservation pilot program | Fox News
article_summary: U.S.-Backed Gaza Aid Group Introduces Pre-Reservation System for Food Parcels: The Gaza Humanitarian Foundation has launched a pilot program that allows families to reserve food aid parcels in advance, aiming to provide a more orderly and equitable distribution process, particularly for women, children, older adults, and people with disabilities.</s>
